      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OUR LUCY LOU (3) was out of the money two runs ago then broke following some interference but still managed to finish third, beaten 14 metres, over 2040m at this track two weeks ago. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this much better draw. Won't find this any harder and she can take this out. OPALLANE (5) turned in another strong performance last time when he battled on bravely to just miss out over 2040m here. Tackles a similar assignment and he can grab that well-deserved win. FIGHT FOR VICTORY (9) has been thereabouts of late and is a great chance to break through. Good effort last time out when he finished fourth at Albion Park over 1660m. Top-three candidate. NITRATOR (7) could only finish ninth over 1660m at Albion Park most recently. This easier and is in the mix for some minor money.",
